			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 1 AS is_read, 0 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, 0 AS voted

			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)

2013-09-03 21:47:18 - PHP Notice:  Error: Unknown column 'mem.banned' in 'field list'<br />Error No: 1054<br />
		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 1) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 1)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 1) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC
		LIMIT 15 in /home/sites/buybattlefield4.net/public_html/oc/system/database/mysql.php on line 50

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 1) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 1)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 1) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 1 AS is_read, 0 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, 0 AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 1) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 1)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 1) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC

			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 1 AS is_read, 0 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, 0 AS voted

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 1) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 1)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 1) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC

			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 1 AS is_read, 0 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, 0 AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 1 AS is_read, 0 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, 0 AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 1 AS is_read, 0 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, 0 AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 1) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 1)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 1) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC

			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 1 AS is_read, 0 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,

			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 2) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 2)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 2) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (9)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 2) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 2)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 2) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC
		LIMIT 15 in /home/sites/buybattlefield4.net/public_html/oc/system/database/mysql.php on line 50

			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 2) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 2)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 2) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC
		LIMIT 15 in /home/sites/buybattlefield4.net/public_html/oc/system/database/mysql.php on line 50

			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,

			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,

			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 1 AS is_read, 0 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,

		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)

			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 2) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 2)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 2) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 2) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 2)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 2) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 2) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 2)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 2) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 2) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 2)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 2) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)

		SELECT
			m.poster_time, m.id_topic, m.id_member, m.id_msg, b.id_board, b.name AS board_name, t.id_first_msg, t.num_replies,
			m.poster_name, mem.email, mem.banned, 
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, 0)) >= m.id_msg_modified AS is_read,
			IFNULL(lt.id_msg, IFNULL(lmr.id_msg, -1)) + 1 AS new_from, SUBSTRING(m.body, 1, 384) AS body,
			(SELECT COUNT(id_msg) FROM oc_log_helpful WHERE id_msg = ms.id_msg ) as helpful, ((select id_member from oc_log_helpful where id_msg = ms.id_msg AND id_member = 2) IS NOT NULL) AS voted
		FROM oc_topics AS t
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS m ON (m.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			INNER JOIN oc_boards AS b ON (b.id_board = t.id_board)
			INNER JOIN oc_messages AS ms ON (ms.id_msg = t.id_first_msg)
			LEFT JOIN oc_customer AS mem ON (mem.customer_id = m.id_member)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_topics AS lt ON (lt.id_topic = t.id_topic AND lt.id_member = 2)
			LEFT JOIN oc_log_mark_read AS lmr ON (lmr.id_board = b.id_board AND lmr.id_member = 2) WHERE t.id_topic > 0 AND b.id_board IN (1)
		ORDER BY t.id_topic DESC
